{"tid":1806341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"都6個月啦 捉咩鬼呀仲","createTime":"2020-01-01T09:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T09:31:38.000Z","uid":34515,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8519d113a37f323ff6f0d1615434b4a2eb46807b","tid":1806341,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"我俾你捉100次有99隻鬼 咁又點？<br />\n淨底嗰一個俾自己人捉嘅手足呢<br />\n諗下人哋感受啦 呢個時勢做前線已經好大壓力<br />\n唔好成日捉鬼啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲貼到有人話叫佢唔肯停低<br />\n老實講 點知遊行隊伍入面邊個係鬼<br />\n一陣無啦啦有個呀嬸行過嚟話係自己人 檢查下<br />\n點知反手就俾人捉 咁邊個會救佢<br />\n幾十萬人呀 十分之九都係和理非<br />\n點信你哋？<br />\n<br />\n乜都話如果係鬼做嘅唔通我哋食呀？<br />\n冇大台就係咁 都冇計㗎<br />\n何況反中資都係黃色經濟圈一部分<br />\n冇必要為呢件事嘈<br />\n<br />\n仲有耳機狗嗰啲<br />\n就嚟過百次集會遊行喇<br />\n自己提高警覺啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔理上述兩件事係咪真係鬼<br />\n我只係覺得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬼 捉錯一次都嫌多 ok?</span></span>"},{"pid":"c37f1fad98718f9c498aaa3eecb7cffb026be54c","tid":1806341,"uid":50284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日手足做乜都唔割！<br />\n趁對方人少，往死裏打！</span></span>"},{"pid":"01bcaf4a48f5f3a16ba5e66ceb3232d4c916b708","tid":1806341,"uid":293648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XPNhuXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXPNhuXF.png&h=f63cdfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/h7QWNbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh7QWNbV.png&h=bcc388e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/60Jejs3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F60Jejs3.png&h=45aaf0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/n4mmuf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn4m